Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:34.71,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}那落下眼泪的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:40.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}你本该懂得何为温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:45.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}为何一再去伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:52.17,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}明明只会徒添仇怨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:58.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}历经痛苦得来的坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:05.36,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}定能温柔地怀抱未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.03,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3}不要迷茫 正是现在
